title: VA Funky House Sessions  2CD 2007 Plus Covers
description:
reviews

Apr 2007

&#039;Funky House Sessions&#039; returns with another stellar line-up of the most uplifting vocals, funky bass lines and peak time floor fillers to satisfy anyones yearning for the funkiest in sexy house.
Sitting somewhere between the upfront musical coolness of a Hed Kandi album, and the fun and familiarity of a super hit powered Ministry of Sound classic like &#039;The Annual&#039;, &#039;Funky House Sessions&#039; spins just the right amount of chart success and underground house hits to present the perfect package for any self respecting lover of dance.
2 CDs of the most upfront chart smashes, with Alex Gaudino Feat Crystal Waters &#039;Destination Calabria&#039; and Camille Jones Vs Fedde Le Grand &#039;The Creeps&#039;, together with recent super hits such as Mason Vs Superstar &#039;Perfect Exceeder&#039;, Eric Prydz &#039;Proper Education&#039;, Cascada &#039;Miracle&#039; and Booty Luv&#039;s &#039;Boogie 2Nite&#039;.
